latestPosts.caption:
The Most Viral Matcha Bar in Bandra!🍵💚

📍Tokyo Matcha Bar- Bandra, Mumbai
Influenced by Japanese practices, this place serves the best matcha drinks in Mumbai!

Are you a matcha lover? 
“If this is your first time trying a matcha drink, head towards Tokyo Matcha Bar in Bandra.
Elegantly presented and naturally sweet, their matcha drinks will surely be your next favourite.”🫰🏻

🌟It’s not just Matcha here- the menu also caters to tea and coffee enthusiasts: 
- Boba Teas
- Elderflower Spritz 
- Iced Chai Lattes
- Cold Brew’s
- Tokyo’s Sweet Milk Cold Coffee & much more!

🌟An absolute heaven for dessert lovers!

🌟They serve Vegan, Keto, Gluten Free options

🌟Must Try!
- Matcha Vanilla Bean Latte
- Dirty Matcha Latte
- Cookie Cream Matcha Latte
- Spiced Sambal Bao
- Gojujang Mac and Cheese
- Matcha Misu
- Matcha Tres Leches
- Matcha Crepe
- Matcha Lava Cup-Kie

🗺️ Where: Silvilla House, Chapel Rd, Next to Lovely Stores, St.Sebastian Colony, Ranwar, Bandra(W), Mumbai

🕰️ When: 12pm-12am

💰Cost: INR 600 for 2 (approx)
